GitHub Push Event Notification
===============================

<% if @deleted %>
<%= @pusher_name %> has deleted branch <%= @branch_name %> in repository <%= @repository_name %>.
<% else %>
<%= @pusher_name %> has pushed to branch <%= @branch_name %> in repository <%= @repository_name %>.

You can view the changes here: <%= @compare_url %>
<% end %>

Reference: <%= @ref %>

Repository URL: <%= @repository_url %>

This is an automated notification from your GitHub webhook integration.
